<div class="featured"><div class="content"><div class="featured-carousel"><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/445-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Indiana Jones and the Dial of Destiny Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Indiana Jones and the Dial of Destiny</h1><p>The plot is unknown at this time.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/445/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/446-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="My Sailor, My Love Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">My Sailor, My Love</h1><p>A retired sea captain and his daughter must reassess their strained relationship after he begins a new romance with a widowed housekeeper.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/446/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/440-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="The Unlikely Pilgrimage of Harold Fry Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">The Unlikely Pilgrimage of Harold Fry</h1><p>Harold is an ordinary man who has passed through life, living on the side lines, until he goes to post a letter one day...and just keeps walking.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/440/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/457-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Elemental Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Elemental</h1><p>Follows Ember and Wade, in a city where fire-, water-, land- and air-residents live together.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/457/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/451-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Sugar and Stars Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Sugar and Stars</h1><p>Since he was a kid, Yazid has one big passion, pastry making. Raised between foster homes and group homes, the young man will try to make his dream come true: to work with the greatest pastry chefs and become the best.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/451/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/432-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Bank of Dave Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Bank of Dave</h1><p>Based on the true-life experiences of Dave Fishwick; 'Bank of Dave' tells the story of how a working class Burnley man and self-made millionaire fought to set up a community bank.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/432/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/455-small-custom.jpg" width="150" alt="Cats in the Museum Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Cats in the Museum</h1><p>	A young cat named Vincent, and Maurice the mouse, escape from the flood in an old harpsichord, which is picked up by sailors and sent to the Hermitage Museum. There, Vincent meets an elite feline squad that has been protecting artwork from mice and other pests for centuries. Vincent does not want to lose his friend Maurice, who saved his life. Vincent has to hide a friend, who also has one "little weakness" - Maurice loves to gnaw on masterpiece paintings. When the Mona Lisa, arrives along with a bunch of thieves, Vincent has to show all his courage in order to save the masterpiece, protect the honour of the museum and win the love of a cat named Cleopatra.							</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/455/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/450-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Exhibition on Screen: Tokyo Stories Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Exhibition on Screen: Tokyo Stories</h1><p>Based on a major exhibition at the Ashmolean in Oxford, Tokyo Stories spans 400 years of incredibly dynamic art - ranging from the delicate woodblock prints of Hokusai and Hiroshige, to Pop Art posters, contemporary photography, M...</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/450/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/468-small-custom.jpg" width="150" alt="Andre Rieu -Love is all Around 2023 Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Andre Rieu -Love is all Around 2023</h1><p>N/A</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/468/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/456-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Oppenheimer Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Oppenheimer</h1><p>The story of American scientist J. Robert Oppenheimer and his role in the development of the atomic bomb.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/456/">See More</a></div></div><div><div class="content-wrapper poster"><img class="mc-auto show" src="https://posters.shoreline.nz/452-small-default.jpg" width="150" alt="Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One Poster"></div><div class="content-wrapper text"><h1 class="featured-title">Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One</h1><p>Ethan Hunt and his IMF team must track down a dangerous weapon before it falls into the wrong hands.</p><a class="btn light" href="/movies/452/">See More</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="information"><div class="content"><div class="content-wrapper"><div class="box"><h3>Our website service should be back to normal,</h3>
